propel.core.collections.volatiles

Class KeyValueSessionStore<TKey extends java.lang.Comparable<TKey>,TValue>

  • java.lang.Object
    • propel.core.collections.volatiles.KeyValueSessionStore<TKey,TValue>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<KeyValuePair<TKey,TValue>>, IKeyValueStore<TKey,TValue>, ReifiedMap<TKey,TValue>, ISessionStore<TKey>, IShared

    public class KeyValueSessionStore<TKey extends java.lang.Comparable<TKey>,TValue>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISessionStore<TKey>, IKeyValueStore<TKey,TValue>
    A type-aware thread-safe session storage object that allows multiple threads to operate on a collection of time-expiring key/value pairs. This map does not allow null keys to be inserted. Instantiate using e.g.: new KeyValueSessionStore<String, Object>(1000*60, 5000){}; -OR- new KeyValueSessionStore<String, Object>(1000*60, 5000, String.class, Object.class);
